{"tid":1713632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急repost] 俾人拉咗要點做？？？","createTime":"2019-11-12T18:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T09:23:29.000Z","uid":278717,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"220d8575bc61aec516e2a67d56c1632ac5e8a498","tid":1713632,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:24:48.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟乃法律小薯一名，見識淺薄。不過最近見到有好多手足俾人拉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以決定用我僅有嘅法律知識寫一篇關於被捕後應該要留意嘅事情，希望大家至少有個心理準備，喺唔小心俾人拉咗嘅時候都知道有咩可以做：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>1. 乜都唔好講</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野法律界嘅師兄師姐們講到口都臭埋，大家係有<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對嘅權利保持緘默</span></strong></span>，而咁做係唔會令法庭對你作出不利嘅推定。記得無論任何人，係任何人包括同你一齊被捕嘅人（除咗你嘅律師或者你非常信任嘅家人朋友之外），都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔好同佢講任何野</span></strong></span>，因為佢哋係可以將你講過嘅嘢作為呈堂證供，尤其是可能有popo借機套你料。記住你同popo合作一定唔會有好處㗎！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 請律師</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n律師一定要搵，因為佢係你俾人拉嘅時候最好嘅依靠。佢能夠確保你被拘留時受到嘅對待，都得以記錄在案，方便日後上庭嘅時候幫到你。當然，popo依家好有可能會唔跟程序做嘢，但係無論如何都要堅持搵律師，同埋保持緘默。仲有，當你打電話搵律師嘅時候，一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">小心簡潔說話</span></span></strong>，以防隔牆有耳，偷聽你講嘢，因為咁可能會成為證據，對你絕對不利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 盡量記住被捕時所有發生咗嘅事</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野好重要，因為如果你被捕時popo對你做咗任何對你唔公平嘅事，你係需要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>盡快俾你嘅律師知道</strong></span></span>，並且即場作出投訴。咁樣先可以落簿，喺你上庭時由你嘅律師提出，確保你嘅權益得到保障（尤其當你俾人砌生豬肉或者屈打成招嘅時候）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 冷靜應對</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當popo質問你嘅時候，向林奠學習，冷處理佢哋嘅行為，禮貌地拒絕回應。仲有，唔好講<del><span style=\"color: violet;\">「我唔知」、「我唔想答」</span></del>，因為呢啲說話都代表你作緊供，係可以作為呈堂證供，記住講<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">「我無嘢講」</span></span></strong>就可以。由今日起，背熟呢句，等你俾人問都可以好自動咁拒絕回答啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 盡量送醫</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果可行，盡量要求送去醫院。咁樣醫院嘅人可以幫你，譬如要求popo俾你通知家人你俾人拉咗，同時popo都唔會夠膽對你做任何野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6. 善用法援</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當你要上庭時而你手頭拮据，記得仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">當值律師服務（裁判法院）同法援（區域法院及高院）</span></strong></span>。除咗星火之外，呢兩樣都可以令你冇財政憂慮去搵律師，所以一定要去申請。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">隨身帶住律師嘅電話號碼</span></span></strong>，方便你隨時打電話俾律師，尋求法律援助（或者打俾屋企人叫佢哋幫你搵律師）。另外，假如你唔記得或者唔見咗個律師電話，要記住popo係有個律師嘅聯絡list俾你打電話搵律師，要好好善用（雖然popo好大機會用藉口唔俾個list你）。當然，寫係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">自己隻手或者唔顯眼嘅地方（可以的話用油性marker）</span></span></strong>，更加可以確保自己唔會唔見個電話號碼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係一班同路人好努力做出嚟嘅懶人包，值得一看：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkplg.org/category/resources\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkplg.org%2Fcategory%2Fresources&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=ad071d4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkplg.org/category/resources</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，當然希望大家唔好俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩咁多位手足<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手推呢篇文</span></strong></span>，等其他手足都可以留個名，得閒溫吓習！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有有關拒保同踢保嘅一啲注意事項：⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【拒保全攻略】被捕之後，點決定要唔要接受保釋？</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/127351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F127351&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=eb7c7924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/127351</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有，一些上庭要留意嘅事項：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">浣熊律師Melody︰俾人拉咗點算？民間組織協助街坊上庭指南</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/125388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F125388&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=15926dcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/125388</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">光復香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人報仇！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2353e247ea06acf111cf988478b8ca4a9487fac0","tid":1713632,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:27:37.000Z","msg":"同我推吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51633deaed95f7bc8de46829a573dedbab2d46a6","tid":1713632,"uid":72633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:28:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然提到口臭 大家要記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我冇嘢講 我冇嘢講 我冇嘢講</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea12192e16d0845a0fc620fba7210b25de962e60","tid":1713632,"uid":80851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:29:30.000Z","msg":"難聽啲講句 比人打一身都要我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"65daf03b2d86ef677db1ce654ddef386cf094ee9","tid":1713632,"uid":278717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea12192e16d0845a0fc620fba7210b25de962e60","tid":1713632,"uid":80851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:29:30.000Z","msg":"難聽啲講句 比人打一身都要我冇嘢講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:31:57.000Z","msg":"啱吖！無論如何都唔可以屈打成招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436f8872dd13f435d3f7f32a7bfca8e75c5ab796","tid":1713632,"uid":236694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:32:57.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fe434d2605ff9d40b6e6e8955f0cf350cd6fd2","tid":1713632,"uid":186527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:34:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29ce1fb06a5dad42d686f9ed43a5a9a2d79e752","tid":1713632,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:38:54.000Z","msg":"推吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436d6eb6040771c4d889d6cee2ca6e74851dd5b7","tid":1713632,"uid":137863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:51:40.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"64a6e5d81bfdb55f8f8d6263f682d2491f024656","tid":1713632,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:03:39.000Z","msg":"help pish<br />\n<br />\n由今日起, upgrade版和理非每次出黎都至少預算$200 budget!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713699</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0060e8348549c9f6fc1a828242201bb17666207","tid":1713632,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761e585dbcdb796b4c917fb0abc05b452f4efa13","tid":1713632,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64a6e5d81bfdb55f8f8d6263f682d2491f024656","tid":1713632,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:03:39.000Z","msg":"help pish<br />\n<br />\n由今日起, upgrade版和理非每次出黎都至少預算$200 budget!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713699</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f5afbbf06fab74983e9881a79345c84a285b5f",