,"tid":1713632,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"推吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902a62376dcc68d6b57425ba76e132e579b8ae6f","tid":1713632,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"如果唔講野會比佢強姦毒打可以點？"},{"pid":"2e477f71a962d30990d79317caebe48531063b98","tid":1713632,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"902a62376dcc68d6b57425ba76e132e579b8ae6f","tid":1713632,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"如果唔講野會比佢強姦毒打可以點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"其實問題係無論你講唔講嘢<br />\n佢都會強姦毒打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你講咗嘢佢又可以砌你生豬肉<br />\n<br />\n不過一定要叫律師提出投訴<br />\n去醫院驗傷<br />\n搜集證據<br />\n<br />\n你有三樣嘢可以做：<br />\n1）提出私人刑事檢控（雖然唔樂觀，因為律政司可以take over）<br />\n2）向警務處提出民事訴訟（不過要留意金錢同時間問題）<br />\n3）向聯合國嘅OHCHR投訴（不過聯合國呢幾個月做咗啲咩大家有目共睹）<br />\n<br />\n我只能夠講，香港嘅法律制度其實唔能夠好充份咁保障大家嘅權益<br />\n最好就係大家齊齊整整唔好俾人拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/70284/面對警察暴力，市民可以做什麼？──民事索償、/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F70284%2F%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F%E3%80%81%2F&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=09c5a7a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/70284/面對警察暴力，市民可以做什麼？──民事索償、/</a>"},{"pid":"ff62f3ba19f9cdbb7d37bf3042c1633643732f64",